  "description": "Extend `src/agent_takt/cli/parser.py` to register all new CLI surface. Add `history` as a subcommand under `bead` with flags `--limit N`, `--event EVT` (repeatable, append), `--json`, `--plain` (mutually exclusive with `--json`). Add `--field PATH` flag to the `show` subparser. Add `--status STATUS` (repeatable, validated against `open ready in_progress done blocked handed_off`), `--agent AGENT` (repeatable, validated against the configured agent type registry), and `--feature-root ID` (single-valued) to the `list` subparser. Validation of `--status` and `--agent` should happen at parse time and emit a friendly error listing the allowed set.",
